onisch gewordenen Palastfassade mit ihrer einzigartigen Gestaltqualität.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 04. Okt 2022) 4aArchitektur leicht verständlich. 4aArchitekturgeschichte. 4aBernardo Rossellino. 4aFassade. 4aFlorenz. 4aGiovanni Rucellai. 4aItalien. 4aKulturgeschichte. 4aLeon Battista Alberti. 4aLesebuch. 4aMedici. 4aPalast. 4aPalazzo Rucellai. 4aRenaissance. 7aARCHITECTURE / Individual Architects & Firms / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Architecture and Design 2021z9783110753783oZDB-23-DAD08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG0 cprintz978303562390140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978303562391840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783035623918423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783035623918/original  aEBA_CL_AD  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DADb2021  aZDB-23-DGGb2021